Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.63,0:59:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.96,0:59:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  杰克\N{\rEng}Jack? Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.85,0:59:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.20,0:59:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.48,0:59:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\rEng}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.65,0:59:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\rEng}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.84,0:59:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.03,1:00:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了一个这辈子最可怕的噩梦\N{\rEng}I had the most terrible nightmare I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.17,1:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-最可怕的噩梦  -没事了  已经没事了\N{\rEng}- It was the most horrible dream. - It's okay, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.38,1:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rEng}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.24,1:00:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦到我...\N{\rEng}I dreamed that I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.99,1:00:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你和丹尼\N{\rEng}that I killed you and Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.09,1:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不只是杀死了你们\N{\rEng}But I didn't just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.76,1:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我还将你们剁成碎块\N{\rEng}I cut you up into little pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.98,1:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.22,1:00:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是疯了\N{\rEng}I must be losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.09,1:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\N{\rEng}Everything's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.85,1:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来  先起来\N{\rEng}Come on. Let's get up off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.44,1:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了  来  坐好\N{\rEng}It's okay. There. Now sit up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.35,1:01:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.79,1:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.30,1:01:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.70,1:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没事\N{\rEng}Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.87,1:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你先回自己房间玩一会儿\N{\rEng}Just go play in your room for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.36,1:01:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸只是有点头疼\N{\rEng}Your dad's just got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.69,1:01:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼  听我的话  回自己房间玩去\N{\rEng}Danny, mind what I say. Go play in your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.83,1:01:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我先把他带走\N{\rEng}Honey, let me just go get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.97,1:01:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回来\N{\rEng}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.80,1:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.39,1:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不听我的话\N{\rEng}Why don't you mind me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.25,1:01:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.06,1:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.16,1:01:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼  你的脖子怎么了\N{\rEng}Danny, what happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.24,1:01:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼  你的脖子怎么了\N{\rEng}Danny, what happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.48,1:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是你弄伤了他\N{\rEng}You did this to him...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.91,1:02:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是\N{\rEng}didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.95,1:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋\N{\rEng}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.44,1:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是你弄伤了他\N{\rEng}You did this to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.53,1:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是\N{\rEng}Didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.33,1:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样\N{\rEng}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.28,1:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样\N{\rEng}How could you?!
