Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.80,1:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  要能喝杯酒我愿意付出一切\N{\rEng}God! I'd give anything for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.16,1:04:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意出卖灵魂\N{\rEng}I'd give my goddamn soul...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.82,1:04:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,换一杯啤酒\N{\rEng}for just a glass of beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.08,1:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.16,1:04:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚有些无聊  不是吗\N{\rEng}A little slow tonight, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.46,1:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Yes, it is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.81,1:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您要喝什么\N{\rEng}What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.87,1:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你问出了这句话  劳埃德\N{\rEng}I'm awfully glad you asked me that, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.23,1:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我钱包里刚好有两张二十美元\N{\rEng}because I just happen to have two twenties
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.52,1:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和两张十美元的钞票\N{\rEng}and two tens right here in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.82,1:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来还担心明年四月前都花不出去了\N{\rEng}I was afraid they were going to be there until next April.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.62,1:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你听好\N{\rEng}So here's what:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.87,1:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,给我一瓶波旁酒\N{\rEng}You slip me a bottle of bourbon...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.35,1:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一个玻璃杯和一些冰\N{\rEng}A little glass and some ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.33,1:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的  对吗  劳埃德\N{\rEng}You can do that, can't you, Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.78,1:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会忙不过来的  对吗\N{\rEng}You're not too busy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.86,1:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  先生  我一点也不忙\N{\rEng}No, sir. I'm not busy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.66,1:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\rEng}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.50,1:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我倒一杯  我就喝光一杯  劳埃德\N{\rEng}You set them up and I'll knock them back, Lloyd,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.83,1:05:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯接一杯\N{\rEng}one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.00,1:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,白人的负担  劳埃德  伙计\N{\rEng}White man's burden, Lloyd, my man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.17,1:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,白人的负担\N{\rEng}White man's burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.46,1:05:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,劳埃德\N{\rEng}Say, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.43,1:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时囊中羞涩\N{\rEng}it seems I'm temporarily light.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.77,1:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里的信用怎么样\N{\rEng}How's my credit in this joint, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.49,1:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您的信用没问题  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Your credit's fine, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.66,1:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\rEng}That's swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.46,1:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  劳埃德\N{\rEng}I like you, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.25,1:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很喜欢你\N{\rEng}I always liked you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.22,1:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直是最优秀的\N{\rEng}You were always the best of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.67,1:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从廷巴克图到缅因州的波特兰  最优秀的酒保\N{\rEng}Best goddamned bartender from Timbuktu to Portland, Maine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.48,1:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是俄勒冈州的波特兰\N{\rEng}Or Portland, Oregon, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.04,1:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您这么说\N{\rEng}Thank you for saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.02,1:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,敬我戒酒的这悲惨的五个月\N{\rEng}Here's to five miserable months on the wagon
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.84,1:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,以及它给我造成的无法弥补的伤害\N{\rEng}and all the irreparable harm that it's caused me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.08,1:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,您过得还好吗  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}How are things going, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.00,1:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很好  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Things could be better, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.89,1:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不好\N{\rEng}Things could be a whole lot better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.70,1:06:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望不是什么大事\N{\rEng}I hope it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.18,1:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.91,1:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是大事\N{\rEng}Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.41,1:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是跟楼上那个"精子银行"发生了点口角\N{\rEng}Just a little problem with the old sperm bank upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.71,1:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我都能应付  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Nothing I can't handle, though, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.38,1:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.52,1:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,女人啊\N{\rEng}Women.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.62,1:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了她们\N{\rEng}Can't live with them
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.40,1:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,却又少不了她们\N{\rEng}can't live without them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.53,1:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,至理名言  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Words of wisdom, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.14,1:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,至理名言\N{\rEng}Words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.92,1:07:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没打过他  该死的\N{\rEng}I never laid a hand on him, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.40,1:07:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.94,1:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我都舍不得碰他那小脑袋上的一根头发\N{\rEng}I wouldn't touch one hair on his goddamn little head.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.21,1:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱那个小混蛋\N{\rEng}I love the little son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.98,1:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意为他做任何事\N{\rEng}I'd do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.93,1:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈是任何事\N{\rEng}Any fucking thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.07,1:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但那个贱人\N{\rEng}But that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.33,1:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我还活着\N{\rEng}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.50,1:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她就不会让我忘记以前的事\N{\rEng}she'll never let me forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.36,1:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实伤过他一次  行了吧\N{\rEng}I did hurt him once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.63,1:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个意外\N{\rEng}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.05,1:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全是无意的\N{\rEng}Completely unintentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.88,1:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那可能发生在任何人身上\N{\rEng}It could have happened to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.88,1:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那已经是他妈三年前的事了\N{\rEng}And it was three goddamn years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.52,1:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小鬼把我的稿子丢得满地都是\N{\rEng}The little fucker had thrown all my papers all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.29,1:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想把他拉起来\N{\rEng}All I tried to do was pull him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.72,1:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微丧失了一下肌肉协调能力\N{\rEng}A momentary loss of muscular coordination.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.76,1:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指...\N{\rEng}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.44,1:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,多用了那么一点点力气\N{\rEng}A few extra foot-pounds of energy...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.09,1:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就那一秒  那一秒\N{\rEng}per second, per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.69,1:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.49,1:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Oh, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.19,1:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你在这\N{\rEng}Thank God you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.02,1:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.32,1:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,酒店里除了我们还有其他人\N{\rEng}There's someone else in the hotel with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.72,1:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,某间房里有个疯女人\N{\rEng}There's a crazy woman in one of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.59,1:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她想勒死丹尼\N{\rEng}She tried to strangle Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.51,1:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈疯了吗\N{\rEng}Are you out of your fucking mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.31,1:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.92,1:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  真的\N{\rEng}It's the truth! Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.56,1:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓  是丹尼告诉我的\N{\rEng}I swear it. Danny told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.47,1:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他跑到某间卧室里\N{\rEng}He went up into one of the bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.55,1:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,房门开着  他看到浴缸里有个疯女人\N{\rEng}The door was open, and he saw this crazy woman in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.27,1:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她想勒死他\N{\rEng}She tried to strangle him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.23,1:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪间房\N{\rEng}Which room was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.86,1:09:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密十频道\N{\rEng}From Channel 10 in Miami...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.05,1:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看《新闻观察》\N{\rEng}this is Newswatch
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.64,1:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,由格伦·林克  安·毕肖普\N{\rEng}with Glenn Rinker, Ann Bishop,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.80,1:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,及《新闻观察》获奖制作团队为您呈现\N{\rEng}and the award-winning Newswatch team.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.32,1:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  我是十频道《新闻观察》的格伦·林克\N{\rEng}Good evening. I'm Glenn Rinker, Newswatch Ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.96,1:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密冬季热浪刷新纪录  持续闷热难耐\N{\rEng}While Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heatwave
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.24,1:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,气温上升到90多华氏度左右\N{\rEng}bringing temperatures to the mid and upper nineties,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.62,1:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而中部和落基山脉覆盖的各州则被大雪覆盖\N{\rEng}the Central and Rocky Mountain States are buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.97,1:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在科罗拉多州\N{\rEng}In Colorado,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.90,1:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不过短短数小时  降雪量就达10英寸\N{\rEng}10 inches of snow has fallen in just a few hours tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在落基山脉通行变成几乎不可能的事了\N{\rEng}Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.64,1:10:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,机场关闭  成千上万名旅客滞留\N{\rEng}Airports are shut down, stranding thousands of passengers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.76,1:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,高速公路被积雪堵住\N{\rEng}Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.92,1:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,铁轨冻结\N{\rEng}Railroad tracks are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.94,1:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多州官方告知《新闻观察》\N{\rEng}Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.06,1:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,至少已有三人因暴露在寒风中死亡\N{\rEng}at least three have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.86,1:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多州州长预计将在明天\N{\rEng}The governor of Colorado is expected tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.22,1:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宣布天气紧急状况\N{\rEng}to declare a weather emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.29,1:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,国民警卫队可能会被派遣\N{\rEng}The National Guard might be called out...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.01,1:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去清空街道和道路\N{\rEng}to clear streets and roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.78,1:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报员预测今夜至明天\N{\rEng}Weather forecasters predict more snow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.12,1:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,会有更多降雪及强风\N{\rEng}and heavy winds tonight and tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.31,1:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,气温将会降到零华氏度以下\N{\rEng}with temperatures dropping well below zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.08,1:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,佛罗里达南部这里  我们的问题正相反\N{\rEng}Back here in south Florida, we've got the opposite problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.40,1:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,温度和湿度预计会上升\N{\rEng}The heat and humidity are supposed to climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.94,1:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,本地海滩将人满为患\N{\rEng}Local beaches should be jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.09,1:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的天气专家沃特·克罗莱斯\N{\rEng}Our weather expert, Walter Cronice...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.32,1:11:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后将在《新闻观察》中带来本地天气预报\N{\rEng}will have the local forecast later on Newswatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.70,1:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(281.2,209.6)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}237号房
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.92,1:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  您拨打的电话无法接通\N{\rEng}We're sorry. Your call cannot be completed as dialed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.01,1:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如需要协助  请打给接线员\N{\rEng}If you need assistance, please call the operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.83,1:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.53,1:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  是我\N{\rEng}Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.61,1:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\rEng}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.59,1:17:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到什么了吗\N{\rEng}Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.67,1:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  什么都没有\N{\rEng}No. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.05,1:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看到\N{\rEng}I didn't see one goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.90,1:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你去的是丹尼说的房间吗  237号房\N{\rEng}You went into the room Danny said? To 237?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.47,1:17:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我去了\N{\rEng}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.49,1:17:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都没看到吗\N{\rEng}And you didn't see anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.66,1:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rEng}Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.75,1:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了\N{\rEng}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.20,1:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在睡\N{\rEng}He's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.46,1:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.43,1:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定明天早上就会恢复正常了\N{\rEng}I'm sure he'll be himself again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.05,1:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你没找错房间吗\N{\rEng}Are you sure it was the right room?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.73,1:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  或许是丹尼记错了\N{\rEng}I mean, maybe Danny made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.08,1:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他去的肯定是那间房\N{\rEng}He must have gone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.53,1:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,房门开着  灯也开着\N{\rEng}The door was open, the lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.83,1:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不明白\N{\rEng}I just don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.73,1:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他脖子上的淤伤是怎么回事\N{\rEng}What about those bruises on his neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.81,1:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是有人掐的\N{\rEng}Somebody did that to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.44,1:18:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\rEng}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.45,1:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是他自己掐的\N{\rEng}he did it to himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.12,1:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.96,1:18:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能\N{\rEng}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.56,1:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂\N{\rEng}Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.28,1:18:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦我们排除他的说法\N{\rEng}once you rule out his version of what happened...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.19,1:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就没有其他解释了\N{\rEng}there is no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.24,1:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\rEng}Is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.89,1:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我们到这里来之前\N{\rEng}It wouldn't be that different from the episode...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.99,1:19:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他的那次发作差不多\N{\rEng}that he had before we came up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.68,1:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\rEng}Would it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.27,1:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Oh, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.82,1:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,无论解释是什么\N{\rEng}Whatever the explanation is...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.08,1:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frx30\fry0\pos(196.8,136)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H130C41&}红朗姆
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.22,1:19:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们...\N{\rEng}I think we...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.93,1:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,得带丹尼离开这里\N{\rEng}have to get Danny out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.39,1:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,带他离开这里\N{\rEng}Get him out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.87,1:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.46,1:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说直接离开这家酒店\N{\rEng}You mean just leave the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.15,1:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.40,1:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈就会没事找事\N{\rEng}It is so fucking typical of you to create a problem like this
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.32,1:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我好不容易有机会能做出点成果\N{\rEng}when I finally have a chance to accomplish something!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.21,1:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我好不容易一心扑在写作上\N{\rEng}When I'm really into my work!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.12,1:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我现在回博尔德\N{\rEng}I could really write my own ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.45,1:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以随心所欲了  是吗\N{\rEng}if I went back to Boulder now, couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.27,1:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给车道铲雪  在洗车场打工\N{\rEng}Shoveling out driveways, work in a car wash.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.97,1:20:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得这些工作很好是吗  -杰克\N{\rEng}- Any of that appeal to you? - Jack...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.25,1:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂  我一直都在纵容你搞砸我的人生\N{\rEng}Wendy, I have let you fuck up my life so far,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.21,1:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但我绝不允许你搞砸我这次的机会\N{\rEng}but I am not going to let you fuck this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.83,1:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  这里是林业局\N{\rEng}Good evening. Forest Service.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.79,1:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我叫迪克·哈洛兰\N{\rEng}Hello, my name is Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.43,1:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是眺望酒店的厨师长\N{\rEng}I'm the head chef up at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.09,1:21:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  哈洛兰先生  请问有什么事吗\N{\rEng}Good evening, Mr. Hallorann. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.34,1:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我一直想打个紧急电话去酒店\N{\rEng}Sir, I've been trying to make an urgent phone call up there,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.25,1:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但接线员说电话线路都瘫痪了\N{\rEng}but the operator said that the phone lines are down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.64,1:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  恐怕这附近的许多电话线路\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm afraid a lot of lines around here are down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.71,1:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都因为暴风雪断掉了\N{\rEng}due to the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.34,1:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的  先生  我也不想麻烦你\N{\rEng}Well, look sir, I hate to put you through any trouble,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.40,1:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但酒店里住着一家人  带着个小孩\N{\rEng}but there's a family up there all by themselves with a young kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.82,1:22:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又来了这么大的暴风雪\N{\rEng}and with this storm and everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.67,1:22:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能拜托你用无线电联系一下他们\N{\rEng}I'd sure appreciate it if you'd give them a call on your radio
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.74,1:22:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确保没出什么事\N{\rEng}just to see if everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.20,1:22:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意帮这个忙  先生\N{\rEng}I'll be glad to do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.83,1:22:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你等20分钟后再打过来吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you call me back in about 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.83,1:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你  我会的\N{\rEng}Thank you very much. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.95,1:22:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那先这样  先生\N{\rEng}All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.80,1:22:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.85,1:22:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\rEng}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.00,1:23:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.54,1:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开了一阵  不过现在回来了\N{\rEng}I've been away, but now I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.70,1:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.08,1:23:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\rEng}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.63,1:23:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,回来的感觉真好  劳埃德\N{\rEng}It's good to be back, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.74,1:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您想喝点什么  先生\N{\rEng}What'll it be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.29,1:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,解醉酒\N{\rEng}Hair of the dog that bit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.85,1:23:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,波旁威士忌加冰块\N{\rEng}Bourbon on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.29,1:23:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就它了\N{\rEng}That'll do her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用给钱  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}No charge to you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.99,1:23:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要钱\N{\rEng}No charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.60,1:23:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钱在这里用不上\N{\rEng}Your money's no good here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.09,1:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,免费赠送\N{\rEng}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.18,1:24:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,免费赠送\N{\rEng}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.84,1:24:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吧  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Drink up, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.04,1:24:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人喜欢搞清楚是谁在请客  劳埃德\N{\rEng}I'm the kind of man likes to know who's buying their drinks, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.08,1:24:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,您不用操心这事  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}It's not a matter that concerns you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.04,1:24:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在不用\N{\rEng}At least, not at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.76,1:24:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就听你的  劳埃德\N{\rEng}Anything you say, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.70,1:24:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就听你的\N{\rEng}Anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.65,1:24:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  天呐  非常抱歉  先生\N{\rEng}Oh, dear! Oh, dear! I'm so sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.44,1:24:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, dear. Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.96,1:24:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我把您的夹克衫弄脏了  先生\N{\rEng}I've made an awful mess of your jacket, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.34,1:24:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  我有很多件夹克衫\N{\rEng}Oh, that's all right. I've got plenty of jackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.41,1:25:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是蛋黄酒  先生  所以会留下污渍\N{\rEng}I'm afraid it's advocaat, sir. It tends to stain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.64,1:25:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋黄酒吗\N{\rEng}Advocaat, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.84,1:25:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生  我觉得最好的办法\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. Look, I think the best thing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.88,1:25:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是您跟我一起去卫生间清理  先生\N{\rEng}is to come along to the gentlemen's room, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.67,1:25:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用水擦掉  先生\N{\rEng}and we'll get some water to it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.09,1:25:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子你的衣服上也被溅到了\N{\rEng}Looks as though you might have got a spot of it on yourself there,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.17,1:25:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,侍者先生\N{\rEng}Jeevesy old boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.93,1:25:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的  先生  您..\N{\rEng}That doesn't matter, sir. You...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.01,1:25:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,您才是贵客\N{\rEng}You're the important one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.20,1:25:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说真是太贴心了\N{\rEng}Awfully nice of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.98,1:25:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了  我还是打算先换掉夹克衫\N{\rEng}Of course, I intended to change my jacket this evening
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.99,1:25:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再去参加今晚的高级晚会\N{\rEng}before the fish and goose soiree.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.81,1:25:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太明智了  先生\N{\rEng}Very wise, sir. Very wise.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.79,1:25:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,来  我帮你开着门  侍者先生\N{\rEng}Here. I'll just hold this for you there, Jeevesy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.59,1:25:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您  先生  谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.17,1:25:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看能不能用水擦干净  先生\N{\rEng}Now let's see if we can improve this with a little water, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.31,1:25:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  那我就...\N{\rEng}All right. I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.57,1:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的波旁威士忌和蛋黄酒放这里\N{\rEng}set my bourbon and advocaat down right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.45,1:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不会耽误您太多时间  先生\N{\rEng}Won't keep you a moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.96,1:25:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.34,1:25:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人都是怎么称呼你的  侍者先生\N{\rEng}What do they call you around here, Jeevesy?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.41,1:25:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪  先生  德尔波特·格拉迪\N{\rEng}Grady, sir. Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.63,1:26:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪\N{\rEng}Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.69,1:26:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.13,1:26:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔波特·格拉迪\N{\rEng}Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.67,1:26:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  先生\N{\rEng}That's right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.97,1:26:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.10,1:26:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前是不是在哪里见过\N{\rEng}Haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.43,1:26:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会  先生  我想应该没有\N{\rEng}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.23,1:26:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,都擦掉了  先生\N{\rEng}It's coming off now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.93,1:26:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.06,1:26:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前在这里当过管理员吧\N{\rEng}weren't you once the caretaker here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.70,1:26:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会  先生  恐怕不是\N{\rEng}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.52,1:26:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚了  对吧  格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}You a married man, are you, Mr. Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.03,1:26:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.19,1:26:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个老婆和两个女儿  先生\N{\rEng}I have a wife and two daughters, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.54,1:26:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那么...\N{\rEng}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.62,1:27:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她们现在在哪里\N{\rEng}where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.07,1:27:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这附近吧\N{\rEng}They're somewhere around.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.76,1:27:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻我也不太清楚  先生\N{\rEng}I'm not quite sure at the moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.20,1:27:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.85,1:27:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经就是这里的管理员\N{\rEng}you were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.65,1:27:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我认得你\N{\rEng}I recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.15,1:27:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我在报纸上看过你的照片\N{\rEng}I saw your picture in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.62,1:27:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你...\N{\rEng}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.82,1:27:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的妻子女儿大卸八块\N{\rEng}chopped your wife and daughters up into little bits.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.95,1:27:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\N{\rEng}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.79,1:27:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一枪爆头自杀了\N{\rEng}and you blew your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.78,1:27:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这就奇怪了  先生\N{\rEng}That's strange, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.43,1:27:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点印象都没有\N{\rEng}I don't have any recollection of that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.96,1:27:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.30,1:28:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经就是这里的管理员\N{\rEng}you were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.34,1:28:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我不敢苟同  先生\N{\rEng}I'm sorry to differ with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.02,1:28:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但你...\N{\rEng}But you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.46,1:28:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,才是这里现在的管理员\N{\rEng}are the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.64,1:28:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是这里的管理员\N{\rEng}You've always been the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.47,1:28:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚  先生\N{\rEng}I should know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.51,1:28:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我一直都在这里\N{\rEng}I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.40,1:28:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Did you know, Mr. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.77,1:28:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子...\N{\rEng}that your son...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.07,1:29:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,正打算带外人进来搅局\N{\rEng}is attempting to bring an outside party into this situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.72,1:29:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rEng}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.05,1:29:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.70,1:29:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}He is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.03,1:29:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.46,1:29:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑人\N{\rEng}A nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.16,1:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,黑人\N{\rEng}A nigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.32,1:29:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑人厨师\N{\rEng}A nigger cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.49,1:29:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做到\N{\rEng}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.07,1:29:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子拥有一种超凡的才能\N{\rEng}Your son has a very great talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.03,1:29:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还不清楚那究竟有多超凡\N{\rEng}I don't think you are aware how great it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.22,1:29:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但他正打算使用这一才能\N{\rEng}but he is attempting to use that very talent
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.68,1:29:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,违背你的意愿\N{\rEng}against your will.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.23,1:30:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他的确是个任性的孩子\N{\rEng}He is a very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.80,1:30:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Indeed he is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.40,1:30:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一个非常任性的孩子\N{\rEng}A very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.47,1:30:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一个非常调皮的孩子\N{\rEng}A rather naughty boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.71,1:30:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请恕我大胆直言  先生\N{\rEng}if I may be so bold, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.30,1:30:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为他的母亲\N{\rEng}It's his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.14,1:30:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她喜欢胡乱干预\N{\rEng}She interferes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.85,1:30:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,或许该好好跟他们谈谈了\N{\rEng}Perhaps they need a good talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.18,1:30:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你别介意我这么说\N{\rEng}If you don't mind my saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.80,1:31:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或许要采取更严厉的手段\N{\rEng}Perhaps a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.83,1:31:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的两个女儿  先生\N{\rEng}My girls, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.15,1:31:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她们一开始毫不关心眺望酒店\N{\rEng}they didn't care for the Overlook at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.78,1:31:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个还偷了一盒火柴\N{\rEng}One of them actually stole a pack of matches
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.14,1:31:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想要放火烧了这里\N{\rEng}and tried to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.72,1:31:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我纠正了她们  先生\N{\rEng}But I corrected them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.82,1:31:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当我妻子试图阻止我履行职责时\N{\rEng}And when my wife tried to prevent me from doing my duty,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.12,1:31:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也纠正了她\N{\rEng}I corrected her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.65,1:31:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有雪地车\N{\rEng}We have the Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.29,1:31:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果天气放晴\N{\rEng}If the weather breaks,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.02,1:31:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许能开雪地车下山\N{\rEng}we might just be able to get down the mountain in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.86,1:32:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以先跟护林员打个电话\N{\rEng}I could call the forest rangers first
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.92,1:32:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们要来了\N{\rEng}and then tell them that we're coming
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.89,1:32:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们遇到了麻烦  他们还能来找我们\N{\rEng}so that they could start searching for us, in case we didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.04,1:32:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果杰克不肯跟我们走\N{\rEng}And if Jack won't come with us,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.72,1:32:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,直接告诉他我们自己走就行了\N{\rEng}we'll just have to tell him that we're going by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.60,1:32:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了\N{\rEng}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.97,1:32:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.41,1:32:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆\N{\rEng}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.27,1:32:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆  红朗姆\N{\rEng}Redrum. Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.61,1:32:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-丹尼  -红朗姆\N{\rEng}- Danny? - Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.46,1:32:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆  红朗姆\N{\rEng}Redrum. Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.26,1:32:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-红朗姆  -丹尼  怎么了  宝贝\N{\rEng}- Redrum. - Danny, what's the matter, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.52,1:32:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆\N{\rEng}Redrum!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.86,1:32:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你是做噩梦了吗\N{\rEng}Are you having a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.55,1:32:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.80,1:32:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rEng}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.89,1:33:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼不在这里  托伦斯夫人\N{\rEng}Danny's not here, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.82,1:33:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  宝贝\N{\rEng}Come on, hon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.23,1:33:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒过来\N{\rEng}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.76,1:33:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是做了个噩梦\N{\rEng}You just had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.37,1:33:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都没事\N{\rEng}Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.55,1:33:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼醒不过来  托伦斯夫人\N{\rEng}Danny can't wake up, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.49,1:33:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.92,1:33:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\rEng}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.75,1:33:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.33,1:33:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒\N{\rEng}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.32,1:33:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒啊\N{\rEng}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.80,1:33:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼已经走了  托伦斯夫人\N{\rEng}Danny's gone away, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.74,1:33:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\rEng}Danny.
