Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.02,1:34:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK1号呼叫KDK12号\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.33,1:34:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能收到吗\N{\rEng}Are you receiving me?
