Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.03,1:34:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK1号呼叫KDK12号\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.06,1:34:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到吗\N{\rEng}Do you read me?
