Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.63,1:34:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK1号呼叫KDK12号\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.85,1:34:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到吗\N{\rEng}Do you read me?
