Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.15,1:34:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,KDK1号呼叫KDK12号  能收到...\N{\rEng}KDK 1 calling KDK 12. Are you receiv-
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.34,1:35:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  这里是林业局\N{\rEng}Good evening. Forest service.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.27,1:35:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  又是我  迪克·哈洛兰\N{\rEng}Hello. This is Dick Hallorann again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.78,1:35:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前打过电话  询问眺望酒店的人是否平安\N{\rEng}I called a while ago about the folks at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.03,1:35:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.09,1:35:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尝试用无线电联系他们好几次\N{\rEng}We tried to contact them several times by radio
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.32,1:35:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们没回复\N{\rEng}but they didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.08,1:35:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们把无线电关了\N{\rEng}Maybe they got their radio turned off
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.73,1:35:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或是他们恰好在一个听不到呼叫的地方\N{\rEng}or they are in a place where they can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.91,1:35:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你希望  我很乐意待会儿再试试\N{\rEng}If you'd like, I'd be glad to try again later on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.48,1:35:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很好心\N{\rEng}That's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.65,1:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚点再打给你\N{\rEng}I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.54,1:35:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.45,1:35:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,152)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs30\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HFFFFFF&}早上8点
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.69,1:36:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请问一下  女士  我们几点能到丹佛\N{\rEng}Pardon me, miss. What time will we get to Denver?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.95,1:36:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,预计8点20到达  先生\N{\rEng}We're due to arrive at 8:20, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.30,1:36:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\rEng}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.49,1:37:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(210.8,42.133)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs20\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HCFA376&\fad(3500,0)}德肯汽修店
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.79,1:37:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,德肯汽修店\N{\rEng}Durkin's Garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.07,1:37:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找莱瑞\N{\rEng}Can I speak to Larry?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.33,1:37:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是\N{\rEng}Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.56,1:37:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  莱瑞  我是迪克  迪克·哈洛兰\N{\rEng}Hi, Larry. This is Dick. Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.29,1:37:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克  你还好吗\N{\rEng}Dick! How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.20,1:37:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你那里天气如何\N{\rEng}How's the weather down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.77,1:37:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在佛罗里达  莱瑞\N{\rEng}I'm not in Florida, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.85,1:37:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在在斯台普顿机场给你打电话\N{\rEng}I'm calling from Stapleton Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.28,1:37:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑到那里干什么\N{\rEng}What the hell are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.31,1:37:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚从迈阿密飞来  今天得赶去眺望酒店\N{\rEng}I just got in from Miami. I got to get to the Overlook today.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.96,1:37:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的天气怎么样\N{\rEng}What's the weather like there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.06,1:38:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,城里一直用扫雪机清除路面上的雪\N{\rEng}The snowplows are keeping things moving in town...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.34,1:38:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但山路全被雪封住了\N{\rEng}but the mountain roads are blocked.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.85,1:38:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得开雪地车才能上山了\N{\rEng}Then I'm going to need a Snowcat to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.77,1:38:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我找一辆吗\N{\rEng}Can you fix me up with one?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.80,1:38:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么要紧事  你非得今天上山\N{\rEng}What's the big deal about getting there today...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.05,1:38:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其天气还这么糟\N{\rEng}especially in this kind of weather?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.46,1:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,莱瑞  私下里跟你说\N{\rEng}Larry, just between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.24,1:38:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看守酒店的那家人\N{\rEng}we got a very serious problem with the people
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.70,1:38:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有重大问题\N{\rEng}who are taking care of the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.67,1:38:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到他们是完全靠不住的混蛋\N{\rEng}They turned out to be completely unreliable assholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.61,1:38:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,乌尔曼昨晚打给我\N{\rEng}Ullman phoned me last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.68,1:38:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我上山去酒店一趟\N{\rEng}And I'm supposed to go up there
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.74,1:38:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看看是否需要换掉他们\N{\rEng}and find out if they have to be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.55,1:38:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你过来这里要花多长时间\N{\rEng}How long will it take you to get up here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.84,1:38:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大约五小时\N{\rEng}About five hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.74,1:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在机场这里租一辆车\N{\rEng}I'm going to rent a car here at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.52,1:38:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好  迪克  我会帮你准备好的\N{\rEng}Okay, Dick, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.66,1:38:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太谢谢你了  莱瑞  感激不尽\N{\rEng}Thanks a lot, Larry. I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.52,1:38:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气  小心驾驶\N{\rEng}That's all right. Drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.83,1:38:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,各位早上好\N{\rEng}Well, good morning to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.63,1:38:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎收听丹佛KHOW63台  我们是哈尔和查理\N{\rEng}You're with Hal and Charlie on Radio 63, KHOW, Denver.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.45,1:38:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,查理  今天天气真的糟透了\N{\rEng}And Charlie, we have what you call your bad day out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.25,1:38:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在天降大雪\N{\rEng}What you call your heavy snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.21,1:38:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,整个丹佛地区都在下大雪\N{\rEng}snowing hard throughout the Denver metro area.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.87,1:39:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很多山路...\N{\rEng}Many mountain passes...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.32,1:39:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,狼溪和红山山路都已封闭\N{\rEng}Wolf Creek and Red Mountain passes are already closed...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.49,1:39:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,艾森豪威尔隧道也已封闭\N{\rEng}and the chain law is in effect right now at the Eisenhower Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.09,1:39:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,据新闻部门刚刚的消息\N{\rEng}I guess as we've just heard from the news forecast,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.48,1:39:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只有寥寥几个航班在斯台普顿机场降落\N{\rEng}only a few flights are landing at Stapleton Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.14,1:39:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雪这么早就开始侵袭\N{\rEng}and, with these early storms like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.94,1:39:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计一小时内整个机场都会关闭\N{\rEng}I guess the entire airport will probably be closed within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.29,1:39:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  他们没有做好应对准备\N{\rEng}Yeah, they're just not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.23,1:39:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雪会持续一整天\N{\rEng}The storm will continue through the day
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.14,1:39:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,国家气象局\N{\rEng}and the National Weather Service
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.48,1:39:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,已向市区外围所有地区的\N{\rEng}has declared a stockman's and traveler's advisory
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.02,1:39:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,畜牧业者和旅客发布警报\N{\rEng}for all areas outlying the Denver metro region.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.99,1:39:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把牛都赶进棚里\N{\rEng}Get the cows in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.28,1:39:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  很多商业...\N{\rEng}There you go.  Many businesses...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.67,1:39:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rEng}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.86,1:39:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你先听我说  好吗\N{\rEng}Listen to me for a minute, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.26,1:40:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找爸爸谈一下\N{\rEng}I'm just going to go and talk to Daddy for a few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.98,1:40:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快就回来\N{\rEng}and I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.13,1:40:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你乖乖待在这里\N{\rEng}I want you to just stay here...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.74,1:40:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看卡通片  好吗\N{\rEng}and watch your cartoons, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.36,1:40:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  宝贝\N{\rEng}Okay, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.14,1:40:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  托伦斯夫人\N{\rEng}Yes, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.76,1:40:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.09,1:40:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概五分钟后就回来\N{\rEng}I'll- I'll be back in just about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.80,1:40:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把门锁上\N{\rEng}I'm going to lock the door behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.05,1:41:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\rEng}Jack?
