Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.52,1:55:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  格拉迪\N{\rEng}Hello, Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.06,1:55:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Torrance...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.74,1:55:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你没能完成...\N{\rEng}I see you can hardly have taken care of the...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.66,1:55:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们讨论过的事宜\N{\rEng}business we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.50,1:56:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要跑来奚落我  格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}No need to rub it in, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.25,1:56:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我一出去  就会处理好这个麻烦\N{\rEng}I'll deal with that situation as soon as I get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.22,1:56:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Will you indeed, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.47,1:56:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很信\N{\rEng}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.43,1:56:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我表示怀疑\N{\rEng}I have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.68,1:56:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我和其他人已经开始认定\N{\rEng}I, and others, have come to believe...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.19,1:56:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心思不在这上面\N{\rEng}that your heart is not in this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.90,1:56:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有足够的胆识来干这事\N{\rEng}That you haven't the belly for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.64,1:56:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会证明自己  格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}Just give me one more chance to prove it, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.71,1:56:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这一个请求\N{\rEng}That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.13,1:56:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子似乎比我们预想的要强大  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}Your wife appears to be stronger than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.55,1:56:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,更加...\N{\rEng}Somewhat more...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.26,1:56:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有智谋\N{\rEng}resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.55,1:56:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她似乎占了上风\N{\rEng}She seems to have got the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.68,1:56:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时的而已  格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}For the moment, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.98,1:57:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时的而已\N{\rEng}Only for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.98,1:57:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你必须解决这个问题\N{\rEng}I fear you will have to deal with this matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.44,1:57:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以最残酷的方式  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}in the harshest possible way, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.70,1:57:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕...\N{\rEng}I fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.53,1:57:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了\N{\rEng}that is the only thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.58,1:57:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常乐意这么做  格拉迪先生\N{\rEng}There's nothing I look forward to with greater pleasure, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.17,1:57:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你保证吗  托伦斯先生\N{\rEng}You give your word on that, do you, Mr. Torrance?
